    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>X-ray absorption spectroscopy technique that analyzes the modelling of the dominant edge feature, and its pre-edge, that occur at the frequencies that correspond to transitions between atomic levels.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
